Class FlagVictory

java.lang.Object
  twcore.core.events.SubspaceEvent
      twcore.core.events.FlagVictory

public class FlagVictory
extends SubspaceEvent

(S2C 0x14) Event called when a team wins a flag jackpot. 

 +------------------------------+
 | Offset  Length  Description  |
 +------------------------------+
 | 0       1       Type Byte    |
 | 2       2       Frequency    |
 | 3       4       Jackpot size |
 +------------------------------+
This event also resets ships of the winning frequency and warzone flag locations
